Class FirestormConfig

  • java.lang.Object

                       java.lang.String client_x509_cert_url)
        Instantiates a new object of FirestormConfig, based on the service account details of Firebase.
        Parameters:
        type - The type of account.
        project_id - The project ID of the service account.
        private_key_id - The private key ID of the service account.
        private_key - The private key of the service account.
        client_email - The client email of the service account.
        client_id - The client ID of the service account.
        auth_uri - The auth URI of the service account.
        token_uri - The token URI of the service account.
        auth_provider_x509_cert_url - The auth provider certification URL of the service account.
        client_x509_cert_url - The client certification URL of the service account.
